      <title>南非旅游业正在强劲增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/south-african-tourism-is-seeing-strong-growth-minister-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非旅游部长帕特里夏德里尔 (Patricia de Lille) 表示，今年 1 月至 5 月，南非旅游业增长了 9.7%，入境游客数量达到约 380 万人次。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/south-african-tourism-is-seeing-strong-growth-minister-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 17:25:00 GMT</pubDate>
