      <title>7 月 28 日投票前委内瑞拉政府镇压行动激增</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/venezuela-government-repression-surges-ahead-of-july-28-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总部位于加拉加斯的人权组织周二报告称，自 7 月 4 日委内瑞拉总统竞选开始以来，已有大约 77 名反对派支持者和助手被捕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/venezuela-government-repression-surges-ahead-of-july-28-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 17:23:39 GMT</pubDate>
