    </item>
    <item>
      <title>现货以太币 ETF 有望最早于下周开始交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/spot-ether-etfs-are-seen-starting-to-trade-as-early-as-next-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，美国证券交易委员会已指示至少四家现货以太币交易所交易基金的发行人提交文件以获得可能的批准。其中三家发行人表示，该机构暗示交易可能于 7 月 23 日开始。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/spot-ether-etfs-are-seen-starting-to-trade-as-early-as-next-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 16:47:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>约翰·钱伯斯 (John Chambers) 谈美国大选、人工智能和并购</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-16/john-chambers-weighs-in-on-us-election-ai-and-m-a-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[JC2 Ventures 首席执行官、前思科系统首席执行官约翰·钱伯斯 (John Chambers) 在彭博电视上发表了他对 2024 年美国总统大选、并购活动前景的看法，并表示未来十年经济将由人工智能驱动。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-16/john-chambers-weighs-in-on-us-election-ai-and-m-a-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 16:44:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Sambas 和 Yeezys 销量强劲，阿迪达斯上调预测</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/adidas-raises-forecast-amid-strong-demand-for-sambas-and-yeezys</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于 Samba 等经典运动鞋的需求飙升，以及 Yeezy 鞋类库存减少导致销量增加，阿迪达斯公司三个月内第二次上调了年度利润目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/adidas-raises-forecast-amid-strong-demand-for-sambas-and-yeezys</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 16:00:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员加大对美联储利率调整的押注，黄金价格跃升至纪录高位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/gold-jumps-to-record-as-traders-ramp-up-bets-on-fed-rate-pivot</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着美联储降息预期升温以及一些交易员加大对唐纳德·特朗普连任总统的押注，金价创下历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/gold-jumps-to-record-as-traders-ramp-up-bets-on-fed-rate-pivot</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 14:58:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
