      <title>债券大王吸引创纪录的 440 亿美元资金流入主动管理型 ETF</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/bond-kings-draw-record-44-billion-to-active-etfs-before-fed-cut</link>
